  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Making water available to over 25 000 people</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will repair the water pump and filter at a community hub centre in Mathibestad South Africa, providing clean water to the families of the children impacted by HIV/AIDS and allowing them to expand the garden program which will provide more food to them for eating and selling for an income. In addition, the clean water will allow for a second phase of a bakery which will teach the families business skills. Lastly the clean water will allow for partnership for an on-site health clinic.</narrative>
  </description>
